  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Asia. The aim of this trial is to evaluate the haemostatic
      efficacy of activated recombinant human factor VII in cirrhotic patients scheduled to undergo
      partial hepatectomy due to liver cancer or benign tumours.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
